Harlequins rallied to defeat
Northampton Saints 25-23 and advance to the English Premiership
rugby final for the first time.  Joe Marlerâ€™s 77th-minute try, converted by  Nick Evans , gave
Harlequins the home win at the Twickenham Stoop in  London . Evans
also booted six penalties for Harlequins, which scored 10 points
